('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000200010000','Ingrid Sørensen','+47 412 65 803','Tokyo','solo','2026-08-01','13:10','3D2N',1,'After 25 years of night shifts and other people''s emergencies, I am finally doing the thing I taped to my locker door: soaking in a Japanese hot spring with a mountain view and absolutely nowhere to be. Please make sure my gluten-free needs are clearly communicated at ryokan kaiseki dinners — back home that is hard, and I dream of eating freely here.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,36500,57000,
