('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000400010000','Chloe Bennett','+61 438 902 651','Sapporo','solo','2026-08-09','14:45','3D2N',1,'I did a ski season in Niseko at 22 and have not stopped thinking about Hokkaido since. Before med school swallows the next four years of my life, I want to go back — the powder may be gone in August but the mountains and the quiet onsen towns are what I really miss. Keep me on a tight budget; I would rather hike all day and eat convenience-store onigiri than blow money on a fancy hotel.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,32000,48000,
