('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-000500010000','Yusuf Al-Rashidi','+971 50 638 4297','Tokyo','solo','2026-08-06','13:40','3D2N',1,'Tokyo is my escape valve — I have come four times for business and never actually seen it as a visitor. This time the phone goes on silent. I want exceptional kaiseki and sushi that can be done halal, the kind of quiet luxury Tokyo does so well, and a planner who understands that halal-friendly does not mean second-rate. Find me the dinners I will still be thinking about in Dubai.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,37000,58000,
