('b0000001-0000-4000-8000-001900010000','Beatriz Carvalho Nogueira','+55 21 98472-3361','Naha','group','2026-08-05','13:45','3D2N',5,'My mother spent 40 years teaching geography and always pinned Okinawa on her classroom map saying she''d see that turquoise water one day. Now that she''s retired we''re finally making it happen — all three generations, including my daughter Helena who is nine and obsessed with sea turtles. We''d love a gentle sunset moment on the beach where we can give Vovó a small surprise. Please keep shellfish off our plates; Helena reacts badly to it.','unassigned',7300,false,NULL,38000,21800,
 '{"seed_batch":"jp-01","market":"japan","person_id":"0019","unit_order":1,"unit_total":2,"trip_start_date":"2026-08-05","trip_end_date":"2026-08-09","trip_total_duration":"5D4N","origin_country":"Brazil","origin_city":"Rio de Janeiro","ages":[62,58,34,31,9],"languages":["Portuguese","English (intermediate)","Spanish"],"occasion":"Three-generation family reunion celebrating Vovó''s retirement from teaching","budget_tier":"mid_range","daily_spend_per_pax_eur":38000,"hotel_budget_per_night_eur":109000,"hotel_budget_per_night_pax_eur":21800,"pace":"active","splurge_willingness":"frequent","dietary_restrictions":"allergy: shellfish","mobility":"Grandmother (62) walks well but needs unhurried pace and frequent rests; everyone else fully mobile","interests":["beach","food_dining","local_culture","gardens","photography"],"must_avoid":"Strenuous hikes or packed schedules — Vovó tires; no raw shellfish anywhere near the meals","previous_visits_japan":"first_time","booking_authority":"planner_books_all","accommodation_preference":"Beachfront resort in Onna with a pool the granddaughter can use; connecting or adjacent rooms so the family stays together"}'::jsonb),
